$ Perl module HTTP::Daemon
@ HTTP::Daemon

When the following script is started it prints the URL with which the webserver can be accessed.

Currently, the webserver allows only one path: `http://localhost:*port*/myself`. This will print
the script itself.

gh|PerlModules|/HTTP/Daemon/script.pl||

